## 💡 Summary

| What | How |
|------|-----|
| **Install once** | Git, Python 3.11+, Node.js 18+, Ollama |
| **Pull model once** | `ollama pull gemma3:1b` |
| **Backend deps once** | `cd backend && python -m venv venv && venv\Scripts\activate && pip install -r requirements.txt` |
| **Frontend deps once** | `cd frontend && npm install` |
| **Create .env once** | `copy .env.example .env` (in backend/) |
| **Run every time** | 3 terminals: Ollama serve → Backend uvicorn → Frontend npm run dev |
